snippet.title: This is the poop that flushed Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s marriage away | Page Six Celebrity News
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's “disgusted” maid described in court Tuesday how she found poop in the bed the actor shared with then-wife Amber Heard — and has the photos to prove it. Depp has accused Heard of pooping in the bed as a “prank” after the actress’s 30th birthday party on April 21, 2016, following a fight between the pair.
